						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/democracy/" rel="tag">democracy</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/filter-bubble/" rel="tag">Filter bubble</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/google/" rel="tag">Google</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/psychology-2/" rel="tag">psychology</a></span>					</p>
